Mauritius Unemployment Rate Increased to 7.2% in Fourth Quarter From 6.3%

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-03-29T05:42:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/mauritius-unemployment-rate-increased-to-7-2-in-fourth-quarter-from-6-3-.html
Mauritius’s unemployment rate
increased to 7.2 percent in the fourth quarter from 6.3 percent
a year earlier, the country’s Port Louis-based statistics agency
said in a statement on its website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gordon Bell at 
 gbell16@bloomberg.net  